  Source:
    Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Locus: XI iii
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The One and the Many
---
Just as the Sun, though one, appears as many when reflected in many vessels of
water, so does the one Atman, reflected in many individuals, appear to be
manifold.
